race.description: Gosford Air - Heat Of The Rising Star Handicap (C1)
race.comment: MYRIAD (10) came back from a seven-month spell with a dominant maiden win over 1000m at Port Macquarie a fortnight ago. Faces a far tougher assignment this time but drops 4.5kgs with the claim and draws the fence to offset. Lightly raced and can go to this next level. COLUMBIA BLUE (2) is back from a 24-week spell. Raced just three times in the maiden campaign and was in the money on each occasion. Best effort was his last run when runner-up over 1000m at the Kensington track where he led for the judge. Two recent trials will have him ready to run well. PRIZE WRITER (7) started favourite and fell in on debut at Gosford recently. Should benefit greatly from that run and improve into this. The ultra consistent HARLEX (1) is first-up after a 130-day spell. Always a threat in this sort of race. Market watch on SAPLING (8) first-up and now in a new yard. Trialling most impressively so she looks to have settled in well.
